If you're brought up in a distorted environment, which

24:05.540 --> 24:09.660
we all live in today, any judge that wraps the gavel

24:09.660 --> 24:12.620
and says, 30 years is an ignoramus

24:12.620 --> 24:15.460
because he has no idea of the factors that

24:15.460 --> 24:17.380
