If we consider at some time, which society will,

25:06.380 --> 25:10.020
at a later time, I hope it would be sooner,

25:10.020 --> 25:13.540
that all of the earth become the common heritage

25:13.540 --> 25:17.700
of all nations, all of the resource of the earth,

