27:15.780 --> 27:18.340
I don't care whether you're a Democrat or Republican.

27:18.340 --> 27:20.140
They don't have the value system

27:20.140 --> 27:23.980
to solve these problems that exist.

27:23.980 --> 27:26.300
They are not educated in that way.

