30:02.740 --> 30:05.460
Well, the police wouldn't like that.

30:05.460 --> 30:08.180
But how many violations do you think you'd have?

30:08.180 --> 30:10.460
There are better ways than that.

30:10.460 --> 30:13.340
You just make a car intelligent.

30:13.340 --> 30:15.260
Well, here's what that means.

30:15.260 --> 30:18.540
