30:53.140 --> 30:55.420
I'll tell you why they leave it out of machines,

30:55.420 --> 30:58.220
because it doesn't work.

30:58.220 --> 31:01.020
Human emotions that you learn are the most significant

31:01.020 --> 31:05.780
