31:23.420 --> 31:24.820
that's caring.

31:24.820 --> 31:26.060
That's love.

31:26.060 --> 31:31.700
Love is transforming all of the verbal and paper

31:31.700 --> 31:35.580
proclamations to a way of life.

31:35.580 --> 31:38.060
The shameful thing about our century

31:38.060 --> 31:42.340
is that there was only one Edison, one Louis Pasteur,

31:42.340 --> 31:46.220
one Nikolai Tesla, one Madame Curie.

31:46.220 --> 31:49.900
